data.text:
2016 (Volleyball) - Season Stats - Enhanced Stats Sidelined most of the season due to injury…appeared in one match and played two sets against Occidental on Sept. 27...inducted into the CLU Scholar-Athlete Society for the second time.

2015 (Volleyball) - Season Stats - Enhanced Stats Appeared in seven matches and eight sets during her freshman campaign…made her CLU debut against Carthage on Sept. 5 and played two sets while recording a dig and one block…finished the season with three digs...inducted into the CLU Scholar-Athlete Society for the first time.

West Orange High School

Graduated from West Orange HS in 2015…was a member of the volleyball team…her junior and senior year she was the highest rated passer, most career digs, highest team serving percentage, was Bright House Athlete of the Week…was team captain her senior year and was named All-Metro League her junior year.

Personal

Full name: CJ Ewing O’Brien…born May 29, 1997 in Indianapolis, Ind.…parents are Kurt and Dottie…has three brothers, Colby, Noah and Cooper…family is currently residing in Windermere, Fla.…greatest personal sports moment was helping lead her high school team to the first district victory since 1997 during her senior year.
